If I am not mistaken, this will return true when the parser is already at a field name and I'm not sure that's what we want?
Maybe the last few lines of this method should be:
        if (token == XContentParser.Token.START_OBJECT) {
            return parser.nextToken() == Token.FIELD_NAME;
        } else {
            return false;
        }

